hwr = wthr.HourlyWeatherReport(lat=self.lat, lon=self.lon, date=self.day,
    time=self.time)
self.session.add(hwr)
self.session.commit()
proqu, reqque, resque = mul.Queue(), mul.Queue(), mul.Queue()
args = None, proqu, reqque, resque
self.assertTrue(wthr.process_request(args) is None)
req = wthr.WeatherRequest(lat=self.lat, lon=self.lon, date=self.day,
    zipcode=None)
args = req, proqu, reqque, resque
resque.put(dict(pid=os.getpid(), response=dict(zipcode=self.zipcode)))
t = wthr.process_request(args)
self.assertTrue(all(c in t.keys() for c in ['report', 'hits', 'misses']))
self.assertTrue(t['hits'] == 1 and t['misses'] == 0)
